cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with human pose estimation from videos using deep learning techniques, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) and Recurrent Neural Networks (RNN) with Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) units. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses the use of memory cells in the LSTM and provides insights on their benefits, which could potentially fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category. Additionally, the paper deals with video processing (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) applications, which could also be relevant categories.
